Oky, first of all this forum will be a closed forum expressing exclusivly for the rules of this board. There wont be alot of rules but these we feel are needed so that there is not alot of garbage going on the board, that has no use or funtion other then to offend others and I'll not have that on this board...<br>
<br>
<br>
Rule No. 1: Profanity<br>
Over use of profanity and obsenities is greatly frowned apone, We feel there is no place for that sort of communication on this board or in RPGs as a general rule. If you can not post or communicate on this board without the over use of profanity or vulgarity your post maybe edited or delete, continuing to post in such manner will result in banning this might not be a popular rule but I'd rather see constructive communications and post going up on this board not grabage...<br>
<br>
Rule No. 2: Flames<br>
On Flames we'll not delete anf as long as they are within this rule and do not violate the 1st rule, how ever if they do violate this rule they will be removed from this board and further posting of that sort from any single user will result in banning. Now we know from time to time there will be problemds that arise nothing ever goes pertect all the time, thou so should you have a complant then try to do so in a constructive way to post. If your a player outside the guild and have a problem with this guild then please post the problem in a polite constructive manner, you might be surprised the result are of alittle common politness and respect. If your a member if this guild you had best post in a proper manner befiting a Champion Eternal member, and we'll expect better behavor from guild members. If your simply a Player with a problem with this guild the same thing applies to you on posting, so use your brains when posting. In final when posting a complant please do so with politness and respect, and as soon as an officer is In-Game that can handle the problem they will speak to you...<br>
<br>
Rule No. 3: Threating Conduct<br>
This rule applies to any post that openly state threating and hostile conduct to members if the guild, the guild as a whole or anyone from the guild to anyone withing it out outside it. Life is FAR to short to be streesing over grabage that happens within a Online Game, and to those posting such conduct we can only say this GET A LIFE please. Any posts that are seen and found to voilate this rule will be delated and or reported to EZ Board officials (in the case of RL (Real Life) threats of bodily harm or other wise) and possible banning of user / poster, as this sort of thing has NO place on this board at all and will be handle swiftly no exceptions. So think before you post please...<br>
<br>
Rule No. 4: Offensive Behavor<br>
This rule reffers to the use of behavor thats not even expecting in RL (Real Life) such as the use of racial slurs, grossly offensive comments and anbd /or overtly explicit vulgarity of a sextual nature. This rule mainly applies to the open forums but not limited to them, posts found to offend the majority will be delated and approprate actions taken to stop such posts. This rule is more slanted to comments that are of a intended hostile nature ment to offend and emotionally injury the targeted party or parties, post of this sort will get imideate attention to be sure we feel these sort of thing totally inappropreate anywhere plane and simple...<br>
<br>
Rule No. 5: Spam / Spamming<br>
Oky, this we feel is a common sence rule, if you choose or intend to spam then board with grabage and meaningless posts they will be delated, you'll be banded and then reported to EZ Board Officials as we are sure they'd be interested in anyone screewing up there server resouces in such a way...<br>
<br>
<br>
